1
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,920
Jiang Yue, wake up.

2
00:01:47,879 --> 00:01:48,680
What should we do now?

3
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:49,640
It's fine.

4
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,079
He's so badly injured.

5
00:01:53,159 --> 00:01:54,640
Even if he survives, he'll be disabled.

6
00:01:55,239 --> 00:01:55,840
Yeah.

7
00:01:56,159 --> 00:01:57,760
It's all your fault for being so ruthless.

8
00:01:59,159 --> 00:01:59,719
I don't care.

9
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,640
I want him as my bodyguard.

10
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:02,799
No one else.

11
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:05,359
You don't even care about your own father,

12
00:02:05,439 --> 00:02:06,879
yet you care about a stranger.

13
00:02:07,079 --> 00:02:08,840
How can you be so ungrateful?

14
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:09,879
Is there a problem?

15
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:11,960
Didn't you always tell me

16
00:02:12,159 --> 00:02:13,120
the winner is the king?

17
00:02:13,639 --> 00:02:14,879
Choose the best one.

18
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,479
He is the best man.

19
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:39,560
Are you okay?

20
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:43,919
I'm fine.

21
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:46,240
Are you sure?

22
00:02:49,479 --> 00:02:50,759
I can't feel the pain.

23
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:56,360
You are still young to lie.

24
00:03:19,439 --> 00:03:20,680
Pain and fear

25
00:03:20,919 --> 00:03:22,360
are instincts of human and animals.

26
00:03:23,039 --> 00:03:24,479
You don't need to hide it,

27
00:03:25,479 --> 00:03:26,840
especially in front of your friends.

28
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:28,919
I'm their leader.

29
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:33,080
I have to be strong all the time

30
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,719
to make them feel safe.

31
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,599
Or

32
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,919
you can lick it yourself.

33
00:03:45,639 --> 00:03:46,800
I'll turn my back and not look at you.

34
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,240
I'll be fine after a sleep.

35
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:33,759
I'm sorry.

36
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,439
It's all my fault to trust that bounty hunter.

37
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,360
I'm sorry to hurt you so badly.

38
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:41,720
His name is Che.

39
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:44,480
He is my brother.

40
00:04:46,639 --> 00:04:47,399
My real brother.

41
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,560
He was adopted

42
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:53,160
by my parents.

43
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,399
We grew up together,

44
00:04:57,439 --> 00:04:58,399
and learned to hunt together.

45
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:02,600
It sounds cute,

46
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:04,199
but he's so cruel.

47
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:08,000
We went our separate ways a long time ago.

48
00:05:09,839 --> 00:05:11,120
I'm his target now.

49
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:14,279
Zhang San and Li Si were also injured by him.

50
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:15,879
Such a deep hatred.

51
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:18,160
Then

52
00:05:18,759 --> 00:05:19,639
why

53
00:05:20,279 --> 00:05:21,439
did you break up?

54
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,279
He called me a dog.

55
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,399
That's it?

56
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,519
He must not have told the truth.

57
00:05:35,079 --> 00:05:35,600
And you?

58
00:05:37,839 --> 00:05:38,680
Tell me the truth.

59
00:05:40,639 --> 00:05:41,560
Why are you here?

60
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,480
I'm here

61
00:05:50,279 --> 00:05:51,839
to find my origins.

62
00:05:53,079 --> 00:05:53,920
I'm an orphan.

63
00:05:54,839 --> 00:05:56,000
I don't remember

64
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,240
what my parents looked like.

65
00:05:58,639 --> 00:05:59,639
I only remember

66
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:02,279
being washed ashore from the sea

67
00:06:03,279 --> 00:06:04,879
and being adopted by my current family.

68
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:08,000
I've been searching all these years

69
00:06:08,959 --> 00:06:10,879
just to find my original home.

70
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,879
Even if I was abandoned,

71
00:06:15,519 --> 00:06:16,959
I want to know why.

72
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,160
Dad,

73
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,199
Qin Yeren's goods

74
00:06:29,399 --> 00:06:30,240
haven't been shipped out yet.

75
00:06:31,199 --> 00:06:31,800
Chen,

76
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,879
you just took over the company.

77
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:36,199
Many people are watching.

78
00:06:37,319 --> 00:06:38,319
Don't let me down.

79
00:06:39,399 --> 00:06:40,680
I'm buying a ticket for tomorrow

80
00:06:41,079 --> 00:06:42,199
to check it out myself.

81
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:42,879
Okay.

82
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:44,120
That's more like it.

83
00:06:44,279 --> 00:06:45,759
Have you found the location of the Moon?

84
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,079
She's also on Black Rock Island.

85
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:47,720
What?

86
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,439
Bring her back as soon as possible.

87
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:52,199
I see.

88
00:07:03,839 --> 00:07:05,160
42 degrees constant temperature.

89
00:07:05,759 --> 00:07:06,839
A bit hot in summer,

90
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,600
but just right in winter.

91
00:07:11,199 --> 00:07:12,439
Do you want to stay here in winter?

92
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,759
No.

93
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:17,519
I'll leave tomorrow.

94
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,319
Don't go.

95
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:29,199
Is there snow in winter?

96
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:34,560
No.

97
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,240
I want to see snow.

98
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:45,920
Don't worry.

99
00:07:47,279 --> 00:07:49,079
When I find a way to remove the brand,

100
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,160
I'll leave.

101
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,959
The epic says

102
00:07:56,399 --> 00:07:58,519
the brand shows unwavering devotion.

103
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,759
Those locked by the tide

104
00:08:00,879 --> 00:08:01,600
are destined to become

105
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:09,000
companions for life.

106
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:13,439
Lu Zhiyu,

107
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,639
do you like me?

108
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:21,959
What does it mean to like someone?

109
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:25,480
Loving someone

110
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:28,040
is that you want to always be with her,

111
00:08:29,399 --> 00:08:30,240
protect her,

112
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:34,480
and be willing to give her everything.

113
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:42,440
That's loyalty.

114
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:51,200
The power of the brand in your tribe

115
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,200
is either a contract

116
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,000
or a vow.

117
00:08:56,519 --> 00:08:57,799
I won't use it.

118
00:09:00,039 --> 00:09:01,279
I don't believe in fate,

119
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,200
only in sincerity.

120
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:14,600
Jiang Yue,

121
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:17,240
we finally meet.

122
00:09:18,799 --> 00:09:20,320
I saved you earlier,

123
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:22,200
don't you remember?

124
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,200
Who are you?

125
00:09:28,679 --> 00:09:29,480
My name is

126
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:31,519
Li Feiyuan.

127
00:09:51,799 --> 00:09:52,600
Jiang Yue,

128
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:16,000
I want to wear this.

129
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:58,360
Handsome guy, pretty girl, let's take a picture together.

130
00:10:58,759 --> 00:10:59,720
Come closer.

131
00:10:59,919 --> 00:11:00,559
Pretty, come closer.

132
00:11:01,399 --> 00:11:02,399
Handsome, smile.

133
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:04,919
You're still alive?

134
00:11:05,879 --> 00:11:06,679
How's that possible?

135
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:09,840
You bit my husband to death on our wedding night.

136
00:11:10,759 --> 00:11:12,399
My in-laws accused me of raising a demon beast

137
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:13,720
and reported me to the authorities.

138
00:11:14,279 --> 00:11:16,519
I was arrested that night.

139
00:11:17,679 --> 00:11:18,120
But

140
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,759
how could they tell the truth?

141
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,840
They just said I died of illness.

142
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:24,600
Like my mother,

143
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,559
my reputation was ruined.

144
00:11:27,799 --> 00:11:30,200
All traces of my existence were erased.

145
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:31,919
Which of your words are true,

146
00:11:32,039 --> 00:11:32,639
and which are lies?

147
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:34,720
How could you possibly be Li Feiyuan?

148
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:36,879
Zang Feng,

149
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:38,600
kneel!
